  "title": "Senior Sales Engineer (Air Compressor)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for entering new markets and increasing market share; develop a sales strategy to meet the annual budget.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with customers to understand their solution and after-sales needs, including providing quotations, generating sales reports, managing projects, and delivering sales presentations.</li>\n  <li>Build strong relationships with compressor principals and suppliers.</li>\n  <li>Assist with basic onsite troubleshooting of compressor machines.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>A degree or diploma holder preferably in Mechanical Engineering or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Preferably 3 years’ experience in selling Air/Gas transfer technology such as Compressor, Blower and/or Vacuum pumps, with some on-site experience in commissioning and troubleshooting skills.</li>\n  <li>Preferably Class 3 driving license with own vehicle.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110981</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Law Mei Fong</p>",
